values: （转换话题、结束谈话或回到原话题时说）无论如何；不管怎样；总之；反正；至少；然而；但是；此外；而且；况且；再说；究竟；到底；好了；可是；尽管；加之；即使这样

synonym.mean: 无论如何，不管怎样；总之

bilingual.target: 无论如何，我会带上我的相机。

bilingual.source: And anyway, I think doing chores is not so difficult.
bilingual.target: 无论如何，我认为做家务并不那么难。

bilingual.source: It's raining, but we are going hiking anyway.
bilingual.target: 下雨了，但我们无论如何还是要去徒步。

bilingual.source: She was tired, but she went to the gym anyway.
bilingual.target: 她很累，但她无论如何还是去了健身房。

bilingual.source: The plan seems risky, but let's proceed anyway.
bilingual.target: 这个计划看起来有风险，但我们无论如何继续。

bilingual.source: I don't know if it will work, but I'll try anyway.
bilingual.target: 我不知道这是否会奏效，但我无论如何会尝试。

bilingual.source: He didn't want to go, but he attended the meeting anyway.
bilingual.target: 他不想去，但他无论如何还是参加了会议。

bilingual.source: Sometimes that's worth making a change anyway.
bilingual.target: 无论如何，有时候改变是值得的。

bilingual.source: Anyway, the next night we were all given another foreign speciality.
bilingual.target: 无论如何，第二天晚上我们都得到了另一个外国特色菜。

bilingual.source: It is not good to push yourself into the crowd who's trying to get out anyway.
bilingual.target: 将自己推入无论如何都想出去的人群中是不好的。

list.abstract: anyway（英 [ˈeniweɪ]，美 [ˈeniweɪ]），英语单词，作副词为况且；而且；再说。例句为“Anyway, Jimmy is a good guy.（总之，吉米是个好人。）” anyway相关近义词有however、anyhow。
anyway是一个中国湖南银河电气有限公司的变频测试产品品牌。主要产品有AnyWay变频功率传感器和AnyWay变频功率分析仪。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, it was lovely seeing you. Okay. Bye. Bye, dear. Nightynight. Nightynight. Bye.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论如何，很高兴可以见到你们。好的。再见。晚安。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, great catching up. Now, who's ready to move on to live penguin testing?
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论如何，来得太及时了。现在，谁准备好进行活企鹅实验了呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Callan wasn't ready. You knew it. And you let him play soldier anyway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 卡伦还没有准备好，你知道这一点，你让却无论如何让他做了一名战士。

yingyinNormal.en: All right this goes without saying but I'm just going to say it anyway. Hands off my sister.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好的，虽然这不用明讲，但是无论如何我还是重申一下，不许碰我妹妹。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, speaking of drinking too much, I was telling Phoebe about that one crazy night after the Sigma Chi luau where you and I, we made out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论如何，说到喝太多，我告诉菲比在∑Χ社烤野猪宴那晚，我们亲吻的事。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, anyway, they make these great novelty cakes in all different shapes. And if you give them a photo, they'll copy it in icing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论如何，他们做了很多种口味，也很多种造型，如果你自己准备照片，他们还会放到蛋糕。

yingyinNormal.en: You're terribly late, you know. Naughty. Well, anyway, Time became quite offended and stopped altogether. Not a tick ever since.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你迟到了，知道吗，小淘气，好的，无论如何，从那时起时间就生气了，它停住了，一分一秒都不再跳动。

yingyinNormal.en: And you moved in anyway?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你就搬进去了？

yingyinNormal.en: What is this thing, anyway?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这到底是什么东西？

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, enjoy your downtime, 007.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不管怎么样，享受你的停工期吧，007。

yingyinNormal.en: So, anyway, welcome to East High.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总而言之，欢迎来东高中。

yingyinNormal.en: And I barely see you anyway. Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 即使我几乎没怎么见到过你。是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, I fell through some thin ice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总而言之冰层太薄，我掉进湖里。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, well, let's talk about it anyway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没关系，我们还是来谈一下吧。

yingyinNormal.en: So, whose good-bye party is this anyway?
yingyinNormal.zh: 话说回来，这是谁的告别聚会？

yingyinNormal.en: Please don't be mad at me. Thanks anyway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别生我的气，谢谢你。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, time to go and be Sherlock Holmes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，该去做夏洛克福尔摩斯了。

yingyinNormal.en: Here, let me make the milk, I'm up anyway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 来，我来替你热牛奶，反正我已经起来了。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, I backed over your pet pig with it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总之，我倒车时把你的宠物猪绞进去了。

yingyinNormal.en: The American people deserve to know, anyway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美国人民反正也该知道。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Readers are migrating away from print <highlight>anyway</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 无论如何，读者们正在逐渐远离印刷品。

examination_example.sentence: Sometimes that's worth making a change <highlight>anyway</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 无论如何，有时候改变是值得的。

examination_example.sentence: Some may ignore a DNT signal and press on <highlight>anyway</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 尽管有些人可能会忽略DNT信号继续按下去。
